pageContext.claim: “People are not being told that the Republican Party is on track to pick up two seats in the U.S. Senate, and epic victory: 53 to 47. The Fake News Media only wants to speak of the House, where the Midterm results were better than other sitting Presidents.”
pageContext.analysis: This is absurd. When Trump said this, thousands of news reports in print, online and on TV had reported this basic fact, according to a search of the Nexis database.
